    "body": "### webpack\n\n*   speed-measure-webpack-plugin 打包速度分析\n*   progress-bar-webpack-plugin 打包进度展示\n\n*   webpackbar 打包进度展示\n*   webpack-dashboard 展示面板\n\n*   webpack-build-notifier、node-notifier 弹窗提示通知\n*   friendly-errors-webpack-plugin 友好的错误提示\n\n*   webpack-bundle-analyzer 打包结果分析\n*   inline-manifest-webpack-plugin把runtime放到html里\n\n*   html-inline-css-webpack-plugin 把一些核心的CSS放到⻚面内部\n*   html-webpack-inline-source-plugin 内部资源引入\n\n*   optimize-css-assets-webpack-plugin css多核压缩\n*   terser-webpack-plugin、uglifyjs-webpack- plugin、webpack-parallel-uglify-plugin js多核压缩\n\n*   cache-loader loader的缓存\n\n  \n\n### react\n\n*   [react-router-config](https://www.npmjs.com/package/react-router-config) 配置静态路由的小组手\n\n### IoC 控制反转\n\n*   [awilix](https://www.npmjs.com/package/awilix)\n\n### cli\n\ninquirer 提供用户界面和查询会话。\n\nCommander.js 完整的 [node.js](http://nodejs.org/) 命令行解决方案。\n\nfiglet @darkobits/lolcatjs chalk 花里胡哨的输出显示\n\n  \n\n  \n\nviewerjs 图片放大等功能 [https://fengyuanchen.github.io/viewerjs/](https://fengyuanchen.github.io/viewerjs/)\n\ntinymce 富文本编辑器 [https://www.tiny.cloud/docs/demo/full-featured/#](https://www.tiny.cloud/docs/demo/full-featured/#)\n\n[http://tinymce.ax-z.cn/](http://tinymce.ax-z.cn/)",
