    "body": "scp 命令\n------\n\n> scp <本地文件路径> root@10.26.xxx.xxx:<文件存放地路径>\n\n  \n\n例如：将本地的sonar 传到 centos 的 /etc/ 中\n\n![image.png](https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/200222/1605844265071-bfe17411-a2c8-4fac-9631-2dbe28173143.png?x-oss-process=image%2Fresize%2Cw_1500 \"image.png\")\n\n需要输入密码 回车就能看到进度条了\n\n![image.png](https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/200222/1605844423646-bbbf1830-1e05-429e-aa5d-26908eb5cc7a.png?x-oss-process=image%2Fresize%2Cw_1500 \"image.png\")",
