    "title": "css in js",
    "description": "1.举个例子import index from './index.css'; const __html = `radish`;  console.log(index.test) document.body.innerHTML = _...",
    "cover": "https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/200222/1608385413259-10c952c3-c792-41d2-92e5-93a8e69c9e28.png",
    "body": "### 1.举个例子\n\nimport index from './index.css';\nconst \\_\\_html \\= \\`<div class=${index.test}\\>radish</div>\\`;\nconsole.log(index.test)\ndocument.body.innerHTML \\= \\_\\_html;\n\n### 2.配置\n\n  \n\n#### 1\\. 需要使用loader\n\nyarn add style\\-loader css\\-loader postcss\\-loader \\-D\nor \nnpm install style\\-loader css\\-loader postcss\\-loader \\-D\n\n#### 2.配置webpack\n\n//webpack.config.js\n//需要使用 style-loader css-loader postcss-loader 进行转换\nmodule.exports \\= {\n  module: {    rules: \\[      {        test: /\\\\.css$/i,        use: \\[          'style-loader',          {            loader: 'css-loader',            options: {              modules: true,            },          },          'postcss-loader',        \\],      },    \\],  },\n};\n\n//postcss.config.js\nmodule.exports \\= {\n  plugins: {    'postcss-preset-env': {      stages: 0,      features: {        'nesting-rules': true,      },    },  },\n};\n\n另外若想在js中使用css提示需要配置 typed-css-modules-loader\n\n![image.png](https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/200222/1608385413259-10c952c3-c792-41d2-92e5-93a8e69c9e28.png \"image.png\")\n\nmodule.exports \\= {\n  module: {    rules: \\[      {        enforce: 'pre',        test: /\\\\.css$/,        exclude: /node\\_modules/,        loader: 'typed-css-modules-loader'      },      {        test: /\\\\.css$/i,        use: \\[          \"style-loader\",          {            loader: 'css-loader',            options: {              modules: true,            },          },          {            loader: \"postcss-loader\",            options: {              postcssOptions: {                plugins: \\[                  \\[                    \"postcss-preset-env\",                  \\],                \\],              },            },          },        \\]      }    \\]  }\n}\n\n此时编译后一个css文件就会生成一个对应的xx.css.d.ts 的文件用于输入提示\n\n[📎yd-css.zip](https://www.yuque.com/attachments/yuque/0/2020/zip/200222/1608385038134-1380630d-9fd9-4537-af57-46b4dee3e5cd.zip) 完整代码",
